---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const title = "Free TOEFL Practice Tests 2026: Top 10 Reliable Sources";
const description = "Looking for free TOEFL practice tests? We have ranked the 10 best websites to find authentic full-length tests and section-specific practice for free.";
---

<Base title={title} description={description} type="article" publishedTime="2026-04-11">
 <Header />
 <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 text-neutral-300">
 <div class="mb-12">
 <span class="text-sm text-green-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Resource Guide · Updated April 2026</span>
 <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mt-4 mb-6 leading-tight">Free TOEFL Practice Tests: The 10 Best Sources for 2026</h1>
 <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">The secret to a high TOEFL score is practicing with realistic questions. However, official materials can be expensive. We have searched the internet to find the best free TOEFL practice tests that actually match the current exam format. Here is where you should start your preparation.</p>
 </div>

 <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12 shadow-xl">
 <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Why You Need Practice Tests</h2>
 <p class="mb-0">Taking a full-length mock exam does more than just test your English. it helps you build the stamina needed for the 2-hour test, teaches you how to manage your time, and reduces test-day anxiety. We recommend taking at least one full practice test every two weeks during your preparation.</p>
 </div>

 <div class="space-y-12">
 <!-- Source 1 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between mb-6">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">1. ETS Official TOEFL iBT Free Practice Test</h2>
 <span class="bg-green-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mt-2 md:mt-0 w-fit">Must-Use</span>
 </div>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">Always start with the source. ETS, the creator of the TOEFL, offers a free full-length practice test on their official website. This is the most accurate representation of the test you will find. It uses the same software and logic as the real exam, including the new shorter format introduced recently.</p>
 <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8">
 <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2"></span>Authentic past questions</li>
 <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2"></span>Real test software experience</li>
 </ul>
 </div>

 <!-- Source 2 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">2. Magoosh TOEFL Free Trial</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">While Magoosh is a paid service, their free trial is very generous. You get access to a full section of the test and dozens of practice questions with video explanations. It is an excellent way to learn the strategies needed for each question type before committing to a full course.</p>
 <a href="/reviews/magoosh-toefl/" class="text-blue-400 font-bold hover:underline">See our Magoosh review →</a>
 </div>

 <!-- Source 3 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">3. BestMyTest TOEFL Mock Tests</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">BestMyTest offers a free diagnostic test that provides a predicted score for all four sections. Their platform is highly interactive and provides detailed feedback on your speaking and writing, which is rare for free resources. You can also access a limited number of practice questions without paying.</p>
 <a href="/reviews/bestmytest-toefl/" class="text-blue-400 font-bold hover:underline">See our BestMyTest review →</a>
 </div>

 <!-- Source 4 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">4. Kaplan Free TOEFL Practice Test</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">Kaplan frequently hosts "Free Practice Test" events online. You can sign up to take a proctored exam and receive a detailed score report. Even if there is no live event, they usually have a sample test available on their website that covers the core skills required for the iBT.</p>
 </div>

 <!-- Source 5 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">5. Test-Guide TOEFL Practice</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">Test-Guide provides several mini-tests for each section. These are perfect for when you only have 15 or 20 minutes to study. The site is free to use and does not require registration, making it one of the most accessible options for quick practice sessions.</p>
 </div>

 <!-- Source 6 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">6. 4Tests.com TOEFL Exam</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">This website offers a massive database of multiple-choice questions. While the interface looks a bit dated, the quality of the questions is surprisingly good. It is a great place to drill the Reading and Listening sections until you are comfortable with the question patterns.</p>
 </div>

 <!-- Source 7 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">7. PrepScholar TOEFL Resources</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">PrepScholar has a dedicated blog with hundreds of free practice questions and sample essays. They also provide a PDF of a full practice test that you can print out if you prefer studying on paper. Their guides on how to score each section are particularly helpful for self-studiers.</p>
 </div>

 <!-- Source 8 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">8. See Guru Diagnostic Sessions</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">If you want a practice test with real human feedback, See Guru is the best choice. Many of their tutors offer a discounted first session where they will assess your level and give you a mock speaking or writing test. This provides a much more accurate score than a computer-graded test.</p>
 <a href="/go/see-guru/" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors mt-4">Book a Diagnostic Lesson ($5)</a>
 </div>

 <!-- Source 9 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">9. Exam English</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">Exam English provides free practice tests for many different exams, including the TOEFL. Their site is organized by skill level (A2 to C2), allowing you to start with easier questions and work your way up to full TOEFL difficulty. It is completely free and supported by ads.</p>
 </div>

 <!-- Source 10 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">10. TST Prep YouTube Channel</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">While not a traditional website, the TST Prep channel on YouTube offers full-length "Emergency" practice tests. You can play the video and follow along with the questions on the screen. It is an excellent way to practice the Listening and Speaking sections in real-time.</p>
 <a href="/resources/best-youtube-channels-learn-english/" class="text-blue-400 font-bold hover:underline">See more YouTube channels for English →</a>
 </div>
 </div>

 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-20 mb-8">How to Use These Tests Effectively</h2>
 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-800">
 <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Set a Timer</h3>
 <p>The biggest challenge of the TOEFL is the time limit. Always use a timer when taking practice tests to ensure you can finish all questions before the clock runs out.</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-800">
 <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Analyze Your Mistakes</h3>
 <p>Do not just check your score. Look at every question you got wrong and understand why. Was it a vocabulary issue, or did you misunderstand the question type?</p>
 </div>
 </div>

 <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900 to-blue-900 border border-indigo-700 rounded-2xl p-10 text-center shadow-2xl">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Need a Personalized Study Plan?</h2>
 <p class="text-lg text-indigo-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Practice tests show you where you are, but a tutor shows you how to improve. Connect with a TOEFL expert today to reach your target score faster.</p>
 <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
 <a href="/go/see-guru/" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="bg-white text-indigo-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-indigo-50 transition-colors">Find a Tutor on See Guru</a>
 <a href="/go/preply" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="bg-indigo-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-indigo-400 transition-colors">Compare Tutors on Preply</a>
 </div>
 </div>
 
 <aside class="mt-12 mb-8 p-6 bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl">
 <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Related TOEFL resources</h3>
 <ul class="space-y-2 text-base">
 <li><a href="/reviews/bestmytest-toefl/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300"><strong>BestMyTest TOEFL Review</strong> <span class="text-slate-400 font-normal">Practice question bank with 2,000+ questions</span></a></li>
 <li><a href="/reviews/magoosh-toefl/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300"><strong>Magoosh TOEFL Review</strong> <span class="text-slate-400 font-normal">Video lessons and personalized study plan</span></a></li>
 <li><a href="/guides/toefl-speaking-tips/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300"><strong>TOEFL Speaking Tips</strong> <span class="text-slate-400 font-normal">Score higher on the speaking section</span></a></li>
 <li><a href="/guides/toefl-ibt-vs-essentials/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300"><strong>TOEFL iBT vs TOEFL Essentials</strong> <span class="text-slate-400 font-normal">Which test should you take?</span></a></li>
 <li><a href="/guides/toefl-score-reporting/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300"><strong>TOEFL Score Reporting Explained</strong> <span class="text-slate-400 font-normal">How sending scores to universities actually works</span></a></li>
 <li><a href="/resources/best-toefl-online-courses/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300"><strong>Best TOEFL Online Courses</strong> <span class="text-slate-400 font-normal">Top paid prep courses, ranked</span></a></li>
 </ul>
 <p class="mt-5 pt-5 border-t border-slate-700 text-sm text-slate-300">Need 1 on 1 speaking practice with a real tutor before test day?
 <a href="/reviews/see-guru/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline">See Guru</a>offers 3 free trial lessons with certified teachers, no credit card required.
 </p>
 </aside>

 </article>

 <script type="application/ld+json" slot="structured-data" set:html={JSON.stringify({
 "@context": "https://schema.org",
 "@type": "ItemList",
 "name": title,
 "description": description,
 "itemListElement": [
 { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "ETS Official TOEFL iBT Free Practice Test" },
 { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Magoosh TOEFL Free Trial" },
 { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "BestMyTest TOEFL Mock Tests" },
 { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 4, "name": "Kaplan Free TOEFL Practice Test" },
 { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 5, "name": "Test-Guide TOEFL Practice" },
 { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 6, "name": "4Tests.com TOEFL Exam" },
 { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 7, "name": "PrepScholar TOEFL Resources" },
 { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 8, "name": "See Guru Diagnostic Sessions" },
 { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 9, "name": "Exam English" },
 { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 10, "name": "TST Prep YouTube Channel" }
 ]
 })} />
 <Footer />
</Base>
